Reports and Dashboards

If your org has Enable Middle Names for Person Names turned on, you may notice that middle names aren't appearing in full name fields on reports. A missing middle name can cause issues if filtering reports on the "Full Name" field.

Work-around: add a person's middle name to their "First Name" field or use three filters:

First Name equals [Name]
Middle Name equals [Middle Name]
Last Name equals [Last Name]
title: Resolving Middle Name Issues on Reports
